# ============================================================
# SECRET MANAGEMENT NOTE
# ============================================================
# This file is for REFERENCE ONLY.
#
# Recommended approach: Use GCP Secret Manager + Summon
# - Store secrets in GCP Secret Manager (same source for local & prod)
# - Use summon with gcloud plugin to inject secrets
# - See secrets.yml for secret mappings
# - Run: summon -p gcloud docker-compose up
#
# Alternative (Manual Setup Only):
# - Export secrets: summon -p gcloud env | grep -E "ANTHROPIC|GCP" > .env.local
# - Or use gcloud CLI directly to fetch secrets
# - Never commit .env or .env.local to version control
# ============================================================

# Anthropic Claude API Key
# Store in GCP Secret Manager as: anthropic-api-key
